\f2\i\b \cf0 3DxCubeDemo\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Cocoa based OpenGL sample application that uses the model of a cube.  Demonstrates a method of processing device data by polling the device status in a separate thread.\
\
