\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f1\i0\b0\fs24 \cf0 A simple Cocoa based sample, that shows the usage of the new SetConnexionHandlers() function and provides a \'93load\'94 (sleep delay) to test for device events (NOT) \'93queueing up\'94. 
\f3 This sample is prepared to build a sandboxed application and include the appropriate entitlement file.\
